data.description: Lovely 4 bedroom home in Nexton's North Creek community! Spacious open floor plan over 3700 SF of functional living space! Amazing Kitchen with painted maple cabinets, huge island, granite counter tops and stainless appliances. Butlers pantry with matching features offers additional kitchen storage space, also a formal dining area and breakfast dining area in the kitchen. Drop zone off the garage entry features a beautiful built-in bench with cubbies for quick outdoor storage, private study and half bath, and large great room complete the main floor. The huge upstairs master includes a sitting room! There are three guest bedrooms and a huge bonus room. Include a two car garage and fully fenced in back yard to complete this beautiful home
